.TH HSH 1 "15th April 2026" "1.0" "Simple Shell Man Page"
.sp
.SH NAME
hsh \- simple UNIX command interpreter
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hsh
[\fIcommand\fR]
.br
.B sh
[\fIcommand\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
hsh is a simple UNIX command line interpreter that was created in the Gates of Hell for a project in C - Simple Shell.
.PP
Interactive mode:
.RS
$ ./hsh
.br
($) command
.RE
Non-interactive mode:
.RS
$ echo "command"| ./hsh
.RE
.SH BUILTINS
.B exit
.RS
Exits the shell
.RE
.B env
.RS
Print current environment
.RE
